# NAME: Google
# AUTHOR: Codex
# UPDATED: 2026-06-14
# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: Google service documentation, v2fly/domain-list-community, Loyalsoldier/surge-rules, SukkaW/Surge, Rabbit-Spec/Surge, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script
# NOTE: Google services and owned products, explicitly excluding YouTube and YouTube Music dedicated domains.
# NOTE: Broad google.com, googleapis.com and googleusercontent.com suffixes are intentionally avoided because Surge rulesets cannot express child-domain exclusions.
# NOTE: Shared Google infrastructure may still be used by multiple Google products. Shared Google Cloud customer hosting and broad IP ranges are excluded.

